{"tid":1345301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢青成日鬧警察，有事唔好報警呀","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:38:09.000Z","uid":28451,"like":86,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1bec4948574f5cf6b4ed1da57c67bc76ba43f2","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"多謝香港政府今次完美示範，報警係冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n警察=黑社會<br />\n<br />\n香港已經接近無政府狀態邊緣，弱智都清楚明白係用暴力治港<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係中共治下嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前講港獨仲會俾人負評，一大堆人講香港人未ready<br />\n<br />\n我07反東北高鐵已經ready, 你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代革命   香港獨立"},{"pid":"79604f95a575c94ed8ccecae7ba06519b77a8387","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5016e48ec53d8caa05db7f0289e0e994af315610","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd029e091e976f0892712bca9a8f49617c020110","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"大部分香港人其實追求嘅係「思考香港嘅主體性與自由」<br />\n香港獨立只係其中一個答案，唔一定係得一個答案<br />\n但中共係呢種主體性與自由都唔俾空間，怕會有獨立呢個答案出玩<br />\n<br />\n中共唔俾人講，我地更加要講多啲<br />\n唔理你同唔同意，都應該一齊參加討論<br />\n討論係為左拎返個主導權同主體性<br />\n正如當年佔領中環都講係「不實行」，目的係嚇鳩個政府，雖然最後都係啟動左<br />\n當然我希望獨立都係一樣"},{"pid":"8ec4d24afb147c2e28b5922aa863f3086145a39c","tid":1345301,"uid":35955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"其實成日話有事唔好報警係咪弱智<br />\n我唔報警你係咪唔出糧？"},{"pid":"186aefe155ea397d8a16c9c6c58740b344f8b5c0","tid":1345301,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"差佬出緊我地既糧。你唔想做就辭工lor"},{"pid":"bdbbd43313a22a7c0f108b71cf474600cbe0270f","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"依家我見親連儂牆都寫一堆「香港獨立」<br />\n增加大家思考嘅機會<br />\n大家都可以"},{"pid":"f9674e0745b9f877308374dabb242595507f7ffa","tid":1345301,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上環係暴力鎮壓，元朗係恐怖襲擊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e95c3a9b9325077bb5bb77c240514c9e8dbfce95","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8751e89e2792bdc8709f9d8478cfc280ff6088","tid":1345301,"uid":106641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:03.000Z","msg":"事實上報警真係冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n健身狗，美容雞，傳銷，倫敦金，電話騙案，cold call電話騷擾，有邊一鑊係有作為？電話騙案或者重可以話難以追查，但健身狗，倫敦金，美容雞呢啲又點解釋"},{"pid":"992a415c135ae2c4937d9ea24fb3db116e5f7e59","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968b39a783a22fc82f755c70cc665201cd2b660e","tid":1345301,"uid":98653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:55:59.000Z","msg":"先唔講班差佬出緊糧，睇到出面好多轉貼，班人甚至班差佬話佢地都係人，平時被人鬧黑警，而家有事要人幫就搵佢地?<br />\n屌哂佢地老母啦，如果因為咁嘅原因就可以由9班市民被人打，全因為想出口氣，就覺得尋晚全部被打既人都係抵死。你班9做乜警察啊？不知所謂！"},{"pid":"d6c2f127a933c9523dd7afb944f5f9387e5ba333","tid":1345301,"uid":140028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"唔係話今次<br />\n其實本身都係無撚用<br />\n都唔知憑咩咁有自信咁講"},{"pid":"1d386987b7fa8b6d6021f5afe615b174d8f244e4","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fa70bcb0fc1cab30ed6e74beea49b7908f3dfc","tid":1345301,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit